## Running Security Tests

```bash
pip install pytest pyyaml
pytest test_security.py -v
```

All 4 tests should pass. If any fail, review your YAML configs.

---

## Rollout Modes

| Mode | Behavior |
|------|----------|
| `observe` | Log violations but don't block (safe to start with) |
| `shadow` | Run checks in parallel, compare with baseline |
| `enforce` | Block policy violations (production mode) |

Change the mode in `.env.protector`:
```
AGENT_FIREWALL_MODE=enforce
```

